if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364fa5e1dc31e1a7ad95e789cd06fbbc161e2d5a","tid":340750,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/203094/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/203094/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n你唔係月入15k咋咩?"},{"pid":"4e1104060cab1e2b583b61f8f42f5b0f525961cf","tid":340750,"uid":99179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我中三開始做地盤，宜家我24歲，做判頭月賺12萬。 <br />\n<br />\n我以前啲同學先岩岩開始出黎做野，成個ON9仔咁..而家見到D DSE雞係度努力讀書話想入U我真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我話你聽你入Ｕ唔係入神科根本就無用！出到黎我諗份人工仲少過茶餐廳Ｄ洗碗阿姐，仲要受上司氣，又要玩辨公室政治。<br />\n<br />\n你或者會話：「有大學學歷上位會易Ｄ。」你都痴Ｑ線！學歷呢Ｄ野係你開始做野之後兩年已經無用，Ｄ人只係會睇你工作經驗同埋你既刷鞋能力而決定比唔比你上位。<br />\n<br />\n話說我公司有個仆街刷鞋仔平時又唔做野，但係做左唔夠一年已經騎係我頭上便。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以你要上位根本唔係睇你能力，睇你識唔識做狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係職場上你做到小夫咁，我敢話你係無敵但係屌你老母！係呀！我死都唔係放低我尊嚴呀！我大丈夫頂天立地，絕不為五斗米折腰，加個幾千蚊人工就想我幫你食屎？！我呸！我而家就唔撈去做地盤佬&hellip;&hellip;做地盤有咩好處？真係多籮籮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一：你讀建造業課程唔洗比學費不特止仲有每月三千幾蚊津貼sponsored唔向左走向右走使好似Ｄ大學生咁讀完３，４年仲要咩住幾廿萬數<br />\n<br />\n第二：人工高，入職就一千蚊左右一日，你做足３０日就有３萬多勞多得。當Ｄ大學生仲咩緊數既時候，你已經有一百萬渣手，人生贏家<br />\n<br />\n第三：地盤佬直腸直肚，唔會笑裡藏刀，比起辦公室Ｄon9仔真誠好多鍾意屌就屌，唔會帶面具做人，同呢Ｄ人翻工，談笑風生，舉杯暢飲好比回到三國，和豪傑張翼德飲酒咁。何不快活？！<br />\n<br />\n第四：做地盤好比免費做GYM，鍾意做GYM既巴打不妨一試，到時練到好似彭于晏咁大隻，話唔埋可以祕撈埋MODEL TIM！所以話，年青人識諗既，應該一中學畢業就做地盤佬&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第五：唔會識到女朋友，就有好多錢剩，日日叫g都得，每日唔同。"},{"pid":"b864d143551860e7712c8a4c7f45af389a095f2c","tid":340750,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬威過威士忌"},{"pid":"f3cc6983ed6a6d41a7120b9f231ac9f6e8fafb32","tid":340750,"uid":19138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:06:46.000Z","msg":"好多人冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e68fe282c5aa81bfc3652bae6f183870c5a4d5","tid":340750,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"一出黎成千蚊日你係咪腦細個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fdbf7eb7e20b84d27dc52472f067b485adee79","tid":340750,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多人冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a6bb0c339f74e2c5d87f814d961cb51e50087d","tid":340750,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/191453_5658c07ecb3b42d8f158fb7cf387c76d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F191453_5658c07ecb3b42d8f158fb7cf387c76d.jpg&h=0ddafb11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知唔知其實有起底功能？"},{"pid":"c8de2f8b378105dfa1431e6aabe412a4d7a9066a","tid":340750,"uid":12960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:40:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇你幾時工業意外死</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cef40f7da19157428821c242c6ca846400100aa","tid":340750,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"一出身就有成千蚊擺明老吹 但係做耐左老師父揾千零二千一日都唔係話冇 不過要去到呢個階段真係有排捱"},{"pid":"078c5b25f2764ded2471025b81f99fff2043ab19","tid":340750,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"又推人入火坑"},{"pid":"68b40c3c65e1a440ed8030ebb3c8c16581d8cff3","tid":340750,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"又水人入地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8dde8f3eabcc8040d41350a13aad3090c10497","tid":340750,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一出身就有成千蚊擺明老吹 但係做耐左老師父揾千零二千一日都唔係話冇 不過要去到呢個階段真係有排捱</blockquote><br />\n新仔都係700<br />\n<br />\n仲話做30日<br />\n<br />\n一個月比盡你咪開27日工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a1cc63cf63ff12d164ff874dbe316008baee34","tid":340750,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T12:05:54.000Z","msg":"篇文好耐冇見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86da789fbec022128b94ceab600ab76ea2a6c595","tid":340750,"uid":3324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T12:07:09.0